miracle in cell no. 7 ( hangul : 7번방의 선물 ; rr : 7beonbangui seonmul ; lit . " a gift from room 7 " ) is a 2013 south korean film starring ryu seung-ryong , kal so-won and park shin-hye . the film is a heartwarming comedy and family melodrama about a mentally challenged man wrongfully imprisoned for murder , who builds friendships with the hardened criminals in his cell , and in return they help him see his daughter again by smuggling her into the prison . the film 's early working title was december 23 ( hangul : 12월 23일 ) .